HEADWORD: Rucervine
<hw>Ru*cer"vine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>Rucervus</ets>, the genus, fr. NL. <ets>Ru</ets>sa a certain genus
of deer (Malay <ets>r<?/sa</ets> deer) + <ets>Cervus</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of, like, or pertaining to, a deer of the genus
